name: Commander Praji (V)
Lore: 'Vader''s aide on the Devastator. Personally supervised search for Death Star plans on Tatooine by Vader''s order. Was graduated with honors from Imperial Navy Academy on Carida.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Once during your control phase (twice if on Devastator) may use 1 Force to take any Imperial pilot of ability < 3 into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
